{"tid":2354144,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"吃5G閉門羹不心息　華為：希望與澳洲討論建設6G網絡","createTime":"2021-01-05T08:51:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-11T03:27:02.000Z","uid":39464,"like":3,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"fe8a6742803a39ee56a5f8f9e55d83af5e6971db","tid":2354144,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T08:51:44.000Z","msg":"中國電訊器材供應商華為促請澳洲政府，開始與該公司討論如何推出6G流動網絡，以免再一次出現華為想參建5G網絡卻被禁止的情況。<br />\n<br />\n《雪梨晨鋒報》報道，華為已放棄嘗試推翻澳洲5G禁令的決定，但現在希望與政府合作，研究和發展下一代的流動網絡。<br />\n<br />\n該公司企業事務總監Jeremy Mitchell說，雖然若現在解禁華為供應5G器材「不算太遲」，但也「不太可能」，「我們現在希望與澳洲政府對話，討論6G或7G（技術）面世時要做甚麼，因為無論喜歡與否，華為或另一間中國公司將是這方面的引領者。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.sbs.com.au/language/cantonese/zh-hant/huawei-wants-to-begin-talking-to-the-australian-government-about-6g-network\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sbs.com.au%2Flanguage%2Fcantonese%2Fzh-hant%2Fhuawei-wants-to-begin-talking-to-the-australian-government-about-6g-network&d=QL2FFPepynYtbGyOTzoAG%2FG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=65d2de1b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.sbs.com.au/language/cantonese/zh-hant/huawei-wants-to-begin-talking-to-the-australian-government-about-6g-network</a>"},{"pid":"3b7ba17d4adf8d077c0d82eab8f7c29b3cf1a62e","tid":2354144,"uid":51271,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T08:54:34.000Z","msg":"華為下世啦"},{"pid":"ca67811de364160446473c51d7c79ca504690955","tid":2354144,"uid":35430,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T08:55:31.000Z","msg":"開大門方便你全面滲透？"},{"pid":"07452c7246327cec142673669949ee8db41d6304","tid":2354144,"uid":35783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T08:55:46.000Z","msg":"揾澳州<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8016af4dded8a8c3cf00d5f5c01ca97068e5be1","tid":2354144,"uid":258696,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T08:56:32.000Z","msg":"中国又要反制澳洲<img src=\"/assets/face